//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Haptic Teleoperation Client with Integrated Virtual Environment
// - Sends haptic device position (x,y,z) to server via SEND_PORT
// - Receives force feedback from server via RECV_PORT (or FALLBACK_PORT)
// - Applies smoothed force feedback with adaptive damping/stiffness
// - Allows free movement when no force feedback is received
// - Displays all data on console with raw packet debugging
// - Integrates a virtual environment with plane and spheres for local haptic simulation
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
